  "texts": [
    "• ToolAlpaca (Tang et al, 2023).",
    "The ToolAlpaca dataset aims to enhance models' abilities to use common tools, comprising a total of 3,928 instances and over 400 tools.",
    "During construction, 500 randomly selected APIs from a public API repository serve as a starting point.",
    "The models are then employed to generate more comprehensive documentation, resulting in the creation of a diverse collection of tools.",
    "• ToolBench (Anonymous, 2024)."
  ]
